#: src/views/yield-dtf/overview/components/backing/risks.tsx:87
msgid "Because RTokens are governed in a decentralized manner by those staking their RSR on the RToken, the possibility of \"governance attacks\" exists. While <0>undesirable governance outcomes</0> are possible, the protocol's design ensures that there is sufficient incentivisation for responsible, balanced governance decisions. Built-in delays throughout the governance cycle also provide additional layers of security. Nevertheless, research on a specific RToken's governance structure is strongly recommended."
msgstr "由于 RTokens 由在 RToken 上 Stake 其 RSR 的人以去中心化方式治理，因此存在“治理攻击”的可能性。尽管<0>不良治理结果</0>有可能发生，但协议的设计确保了对负责任、平衡的治理决策有足够的激励。整个治理周期中内置的延迟也提供了额外的安全保障。尽管如此，仍强烈建议研究特定 RToken 的治理结构。"

#: src/views/yield-dtf/overview/components/backing/risks.tsx:42
